summary:
Adds two small shacks next to Honningbrew Meadery.
Making the area more Alive...
descriptionHtml:
Adds two small shacks and a market stall next Honningbrew Meadery.
I did not add many things because many mods use the area around Honningbrew Meadery
If you wish to add more use mods such as my Clear Stead Farm Player Home mod.

Features...
Both shacks have Interiors
Two NPCS...
One Merchent
A Blacksmith...Wilfric
A Hunter...Hershel

Compatibility...
This mod is incompatible with any mods that change the location of the shacks.

Compatible With Provincial Courier Service V1.2.1

Please report any incompatible mods in the comment section.

Recommended Mods...
Clear Stead Farm http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50759/?
Tamriel Reloaded http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/46925/?
author: Vencent Reapers
